          "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
            "1.  Imam Muhammad Baqir (a.s.) says, “One who is patient and blind and hopeful of divine rewards and is a lover of the progeny   of   Muhammad   (s.a.w.s.)   there   would   be   no accounting of deeds for him.”"
          ]
        }
      },
